":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>公屋+綜援=人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n天水圍大把拎綜援既有錢人，識個fd屋企拎綜援 2,3個月去一次旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好再用去旅行打飛機啦<br />\n有錢點都唔會住公屋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n住公屋先係人生贏家<br />\n<br />\n兩千零蚊租<br />\n<br />\n啲私樓撚淨係管理費都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 無得住公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf0eab5acfcaf00abd0b4b25567a0914f15f6ed","tid":160733,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1289480715a5bde0c0361889d1fd343789bca755","tid":160733,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>公屋+綜援=人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n天水圍大把拎綜援既有錢人，識個fd屋企拎綜援 2,3個月去一次旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好再用去旅行打飛機啦<br />\n有錢點都唔會住公屋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呃緩緩住公屋 點會窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf978a55117b132d4bd5ee4b42535e896dbc8726","tid":160733,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>公屋+綜援=人生贏家</blockquote><br />\n天水圍大把拎綜援既有錢人，識個fd屋企拎綜援 2,3個月去一次旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好再用去旅行打飛機啦<br />\n有錢點都唔會住公屋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呃緩緩住公屋 點會窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企人供斷左已經贏你幾條街啦 人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f8150d33a08d0a5eb744b80a84dd5fcb2de1a9","tid":160733,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:32:37.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩，天水圍咬老綜個班先有錢啊<br />\n早排唔知有個好似做倫敦金個d (總之係呃錢）住天水圍揸林寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚識玩嘅係住天水圍班新移民係香港咬老綜但大陸有樓有地收緊租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca4546c934271e5a3f13a0c59d34816268e4579","tid":160733,"uid":20622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"好彩住畢架山峰😝"},{"pid":"cf66a14a4eac90467b0322aa0677f3b2247b4e77","tid":160733,"uid":83857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9 凈係得天水圍咩 基本上條條公屋村都差唔多<br />\n利申 私樓撚 勿羨慕</blockquote><br />\n天水圍都被標籤悲情城市啦<br />\n<br />\n一個地區點都要有個貧民區既</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nAgree</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n天水圍起碼叫上哂公屋個個月政府有錢俾佢地洗<br />\n深土埗土瓜灣瞓天橋底籠屋果啲先係真貧民窟"},{"pid":"d7ed9458f3c9563ec08ee1ab38a059ca4d370a0c","tid":160733,"uid":68298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:23:25.000Z","msg":"唔通住港島就無窮人？筲箕灣果啲呢<br />\n元朗圍村啲人先有錢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41424dd2e5203b79a5390daf830337072abcdf5f","tid":160733,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T08:25:03.000Z","msg":"人地番埋d現金出糧既工，再去呃綜緩公屋架喎<br />\n唔通人地大把錢收喺床下底又話你知咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d380023fbb546582cc273b9b21b434f6e8c534","tid":160733,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已